title: Dave Yells at Himself in Promos
description: A couple months ago we made fun of Dave for the way he records promos for the show.  If he screws up he starts to get down on himself and .... swearing ensues.  We realized how hilarious it is so now we started saving these clips to playback for everyone to hear!
